Territory of Washington County of Spokane}ss. Territory of Washington, Plaintiff vs. William C. Swartz defendant} In the District Court of the Territory of Washington and for the Fourth Judicial District thereof, hold- ing terms at Cheney, Spo- kane County, in said Territory
To the Sheriff of Spokane County, Greeting: In the name of the United States, You are hereby commanded to summon Chas Wilson to be and appear before the Hon. George Turner at chambers. at the court house, in Cheney in said County, on the instant day of A.D. 188 at o'clock M. to there give evi- dence in the above entitled cause on the part of said defendant.
Witness the Hon. George Turner, Associate Justice of the Supreme Court of Washington Territory, and Judge of said Court, and the Seal thereof affixed, this 14th day of Aug A.D. 1885 D.A. Clement Clerk By Deputy
